column5: I am heading out to do some perch/crappie fishing on Sat. off shore. Question is, hows the bite in Keswick/Jacksons point/BB/ swing bridge?  If someone answers this, THANX! Daniel OCH
I,ll answer your question and not afraid to do so either,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,I have no idea. Sorry. But you might want to try Barrie here.Seems everyone is talking about it.
does "off shore" mean from on the shore or does it mean from a boat off shore fishing just so I know to me it means from a boat but the places you wrote makes me think you mean from shore
